  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个过滤系统的类结构。核心是一个抽象的FilterNode，作为所有过滤条件的基类。然后下面要有PropertyFilter处理属性比较，CompositeFilter处理组合逻辑，还有QueryFilter支持Lambda表达式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilterNode",
        "PropertyFilter",
        "CompositeFilter",
        "QueryFilter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，FilterNode作为抽象基类。那PropertyFilter里面应该包含哪些字段？是属性名、操作符和比较值吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PropertyFilter",
        "Operator",
        "Property",
        "Value"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，PropertyFilter要有Operator、Property、Value这三个string字段，另外加一个IgnoreCase的bool字段控制大小写敏感。Value可以是null，表示空值判断。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PropertyFilter",
        "Operator",
        "Property",
        "Value",
        "IgnoreCase"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，PropertyFilter已经加上这些字段了。那CompositeFilter应该是用来组合多个子过滤条件的吧？用一个List来存Children？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CompositeFilter",
        "Children",
        "List"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，CompositeFilter的Children是List<FilterNode，同时它自己也有一个Operator字段表示是And还是Or组合。继承关系上，PropertyFilter和CompositeFilter都继承自FilterNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CompositeFilter",
        "Children",
        "Operator",
        "FilterNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "继承关系画好了。QueryFilter<T这边我注意到它用了泛型，里面是一个Expression<Func<T,bool的Predicate，这个和FilterNode是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QueryFilter",
        "Expression",
        "Predicate",
        "FilterNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "QueryFilter比较特殊，它不是从FilterNode继承的，而是从FilterNode重新水合（rehydrated from）出来的。也就是说运行时可以把FilterNode树转换成QueryFilter来执行。所以画一条虚线关联，标注rehydrated from。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QueryFilter",
        "FilterNode",
        "rehydrated from"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，QueryFilter和FilterNode是关联关系，不是继承。整个结构现在清晰了：抽象基类FilterNode，两个具体实现PropertyFilter和CompositeFilter，外加一个可转换执行的QueryFilter。",
      "elements_involved": [
